I assumed amirite was another AAVE, based on the spelling and it being a concatenation. There's aintrite, as in "boy aintrite" to contend with, too. There was cantgetrite on Eddie Murphy's "Life," (or am I giving this too much attention).
Any constructor who'd use SPITSBARS, teeters on the edge of AAVEdom, in my opinion.

